This boot designer is fairly easy to use. Here is what the options mean.

Quit:  Bye Bye
Load:  If you have already created a bootblock with this program it
       can load the text from it so you can maybe alter it and save it
       to another disk.
Save:  Saves the Boot-Intro to a disks bootblock.
Info:  Information on the Boot-Intro Designer
Show:  This runs the bootblock you have created. It uses the text current in
       the box.

Easy huh ?!?!?!

